#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.87"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.87:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.87:0.2"
msgid "9. Sītivagga "
msgstr "9. Coolness "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.87:0.3"
msgid "87. Voropitasutta "
msgstr "87. A Murderer "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.87:1.1"
msgid "“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with six qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities even when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an6.87:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

#. VAR: arahaṃ → arahā (s1-3, km, pts1) | arahanto (mr)
msgctxt "an6.87:1.3"
msgid "Mātā jīvitā voropitā hoti, pitā jīvitā voropito hoti, arahaṃ jīvitā voropito hoti, tathāgatassa duṭṭhena cittena lohitaṃ uppāditaṃ hoti, saṃgho bhinno hoti, duppañño hoti jaḷo eḷamūgo. "
msgstr "They murder their mother or father or a perfected one. They maliciously shed the blood of a Realized One. They cause a schism in the Saṅgha. They’re witless, dull, and stupid. "

msgctxt "an6.87:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with these six qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities, even when listening to the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.437, sc2
msgctxt "an6.87:2.1"
msgid "Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with six qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an6.87:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.87:2.3"
msgid "Na mātā jīvitā voropitā hoti, na pitā jīvitā voropito hoti, na arahaṃ jīvitā voropito hoti, na tathāgatassa duṭṭhena cittena lohitaṃ uppāditaṃ hoti, na saṅgho bhinno hoti, paññavā hoti ajaḷo aneḷamūgo. "
msgstr "They don’t murder their mother or father or a perfected one. They don’t maliciously shed the blood of a Realized One. They don’t cause a schism in the Saṅgha. They’re wise, bright, and clever. "

msgctxt "an6.87:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattan”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these six qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.87:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

